<div class="NOTE" sourcefile="articles/commerce/custom-order-categories-nav-retail-prod-hierarchy.md" sourcestartlinenumber="92">
<h5>Note</h5>
<p sourcefile="articles/commerce/custom-order-categories-nav-retail-prod-hierarchy.md" sourcestartlinenumber="93">By default the custom sort order feature is turned off. To learn how to turn on this feature and other features, see <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/dynamics365/unified-operations/fin-and-ops/get-started/feature-management/feature-management-overview" sourcefile="articles/commerce/custom-order-categories-nav-retail-prod-hierarchy.md" sourcestartlinenumber="93">Feature management</a>.</p>
